205
00:11:57,712 --> 00:12:02,915
with three 
carbon-13 positions.

206
00:12:02,915 --> 00:12:07,180
We also have a bridging position
which is a lone position.

207
00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:11,071
There are all sorts of 
so-called Cope rearrangements

208
00:12:11,071 --> 00:12:13,174
where the double bonds travel

209
00:12:13,174 --> 00:12:17,232
